id: pm-ozaf
title: "SDK unified author-time preflight capstone: preflightExtension + assertExtensionPreflight"
description: "Unify the SDK three separate author-time checks (lintExtensionBlueprint, synthesizeExtensionManifest, checkExtensionManifestCompatibility) into one pure preflightExtension(blueprint, options) capstone returning a consolidated ExtensionPreflightReport, plus a throwing assertExtensionPreflight CI/test bookend. Author-time analog of createExtensionTestHarness (pm-jcyn) which unified the runtime-test helpers: one call validates a declarative package before publishing instead of chaining 4-5 asserts. SDK-only, consistent with lint/synthesize/compat (none have CLI surface)."
