resolution: "preflightExtension (compose.ts) + assertExtensionPreflight (testing.ts) unify blueprint lint + manifest synthesis + version-compat into one report/one assert — the author-time analog of createExtensionTestHarness. SDK-only, consistent with lint/synthesize/compat. Docs: SDK.md export lists + capstone prose; EXTENSIONS.md note. Gates: build, quality:static, docs-skills, contracts:check, security:scan all green; full coverage 100/100/100/100 (4966 tests); temp-dir smoke against built dist passed."
