notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-23T19:17:34.266Z",claude-code-agent,"PR #351 bot-review round (2026-06-23): Gemini flagged a real broader bug beyond the initial manifest_capabilities_absent curation — ANY capability-drift finding the blueprint lint derives from a stale in-module manifest mirror (notably the BLOCKING capability_undeclared) is a false positive once an identity synthesizes a fresh authoritative manifest, and falsely flipped report.ok=false. Fixed by curating all CAPABILITY_DRIFT_LINT_CODES from the consolidated view, suppressed only when synthesizing without an explicit declaredCapabilities (explicit set always honored); raw report.blueprint keeps every finding. CodeRabbit: accepted SDK.md pm-ozaf tracker ref; declined cross-module {@link ../sdk/compose.js#preflightExtension} nitpick (file-qualified links are the codebase convention for cross-module refs, matching assertExtensionManifestCompatible). Codex not connected; Sourcery weekly-capped."
close_reason: Unified author-time preflight capstone shipped
